      div.ui.warning.message
        i.icon.warning.circle
        | No datasets exist
      div(style="margin-top:0.5em;")
        a.ui.blue.button.large(href="/policy/submitdata", target="_blank") Submit a New Dataset
    div.ui.segment.reward
      h3.ui.header Reward for Being Published:
      div.ui.bulleted.list.large
        div.item $2,500 stipend
        div.item 
         span.d4a D
           span.f(style="color:#CC0001; font-weight:bold;") 4
           | A 
         |  tee-shirt
        div.item Invited to our content creator’s private Slack channel
    div.ui.segment
      h3.ui.header
         span.d4a D
           span.f(style="color:#CC0001;") 4
           | A 
         |  Published Stories on 50% reduction of C02 emissions by 2030:
      div.ui.info.message
        i.icon.checkered.flag
        | Be the first one, submit your data viz 
        a(href="https://mail.google.com/mail/u/0/?view=cm&fs=1&to=submit@data4america.org&su=&tf=1", target="blank") submit@data4america.org
    div.ui.segment
      a(href="/faq", target="blank") Read our FAQ 
      |  about submissions.
    div.ui.segment
      a.ui.red.button.huge(href="/upload", target="_blank") Submit a Story
      a.ui.white.button.huge(href="/sponsorship/", target="_blank") More Issues
    div.ui.segment
